{"tid":338923,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Cut線從來唔打燈既入嚟","createTime":"2017-07-28T15:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:49:43.000Z","uid":14378,"like":590,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"edecd113b5549fc4dace66399e7352c107245a3c","tid":338923,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"仆街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打個燈有幾撚麻煩呀<br />\n咁唔撚中意打燈就咪學人揸車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1d7fd4860dfdc9c45c5f7a2a6b469e9e370366","tid":338923,"uid":127695,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"有D仲衰<br />\ncut到一半先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?"},{"pid":"ceff67676e62d1eaf5c4d5160d093b59032f480a","tid":338923,"uid":13416,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"好過d司機推左走右啦<br />\n尋晚見到個中港牌隧道口打住左燈然後cut入右線autotoll<br />\n後面部車dup撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後俾油上去望下<br />\n女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e072f3853a08bf81f6ce5700c55311d1d82be84","tid":338923,"uid":14378,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有D仲衰<br />\ncut到一半先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法<br />\n無法例規定轉線一定要打燈<br />\n<br />\n但如果發生意外而又因為你無打燈所導致就係老不<br />\n但都係講句，打個燈好撚難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eba48e0e86b5922a1eafe42a89d073fb0ca0f5b","tid":338923,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有D仲衰<br />\ncut到一半先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法<br />\n無法例規定轉線一定要打燈<br />\n<br />\n但如果發生意外而又因為你無打燈所導致就係老不<br />\n但都係講句，打個燈好撚難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錯請指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37611bdf5665e1b71397ff0d3bc618958257df1b","tid":338923,"uid":9284,"like":2,"dislike":34,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"省電呀大佬"},{"pid":"288c88b91842e19db8ba28478178c85e14a1b80a","tid":338923,"uid":14378,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>省電呀大佬</blockquote><br />\n熄冷氣咪仲慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37566030f72f1c1e18c53ba950393c13f6decd59","tid":338923,"uid":26353,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>省電呀大佬</blockquote><br />\n熄冷氣咪仲慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落車推啦撚樣慳油呀"},{"pid":"522624efe8f8b938bc7b19eda8ade853861c6cfe","tid":338923,"uid":73,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"唱左百變小櫻首主題曲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59717df98b25f7c290996df9acb2e4632a4e733","tid":338923,"uid":390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱左百變小櫻首主題曲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百變小櫻 屙尿從來唔洗手～"},{"pid":"fa173ba63a4f29c98267aa681f3cc912970517dc","tid":338923,"uid":39710,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唱左百變小櫻首主題曲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百變小櫻 屙尿從來唔洗手～</blockquote><br />\n百變小櫻 cut線從來唔打燈"},{"pid":"2d438042b6f01211cb4c3dfd8ad5d54dee42f2b2","tid":338923,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:24:27.000Z","msg"