要收油或者近紅綠燈嘅位都一定會打燈</blockquote><br />\n我自問cut線都完全唔使人就，但每次轉綫轉每隻彎都回打燈<br />\n<br />\n打燈你可以當係最後防線，萬一有車喺你盲點，佢見你打燈都預都你會cut綫"},{"pid":"b7e0328601903599c93130f6a1dcb113a22d4ab7","tid":338923,"uid":57204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad40b3102508d28783d6faf7165c96eb6255e36","tid":338923,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"035fecfa7c324fe406a802225f0e17ab8e391175","tid":338923,"uid":29497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"我幾鍾意聽打燈聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一定打<br />\n平時見人打燈就讓 冇打就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8724d8db36517a12cd059bf0afa93f4b06965720","tid":338923,"uid":72,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"無車既時候就唔打啦"},{"pid":"f3ce59e1609e2498f5b1b3a87ade515b45981b66","tid":338923,"uid":7644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幾鍾意聽打燈聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一定打<br />\n平時見人打燈就讓 冇打就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴士打燈95%都讓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017b4e5edcfa08802feda50be25a2084cf8fac4d","tid":338923,"uid":50336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"香港太多撚樣見人打燈就會篤油"},{"pid":"3819f1ac27ba75f59ae245420f069805aff1e42e","tid":338923,"uid":14625,"like":4,"dislike