"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法<br />\n無法例規定轉線一定要打燈<br />\n<br />\n但如果發生意外而又因為你無打燈所導致就係老不<br />\n但都係講句，打個燈好撚難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟不才<br />\n點撚樣可以因爲唔打燈而有交通意外？"},{"pid":"90897fb5c2c418d2110d054c6683e00e504b73fb","tid":338923,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:38:28.000Z","msg":"cut左先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhea尻我呀?屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d1d85b9963fc01807fedd68c71decc4e5d3abf","tid":338923,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"行路cut 線都會第手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f936e45e8c1c64ba98750292896fd6c40813a","tid":338923,"uid":53747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人 cut 完線會著兩下死火燈比人睇<br />\n<br />\n禮貌上講句唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常都係巴士佬先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame Here"},{"pid":"b849d6a330ca79bf5236fc4bb96e42103087ad66","tid":338923,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"你打燈後面部車俾油"},{"pid":"b0b040a3df1559b310237cb7d0076f2aff48c97a","tid":338923,"uid":67700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人 cut 完線會著兩下死火燈比人睇<br />\n<br />\n禮貌上講句唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常都係巴士佬先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame Here</blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead5668fd5d96d87bb28903fe73ec9a077b8a84f","tid":338923,"uid":67700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行路cut 線都會第手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行路cut線會擰頭望後再陣手講唔該"},{"pid":"15e4d61a1ce4d8f5f9e2e225b888fbdefa56654d","tid":338923,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b8cba914142b99f930ffd3a4af041948e929cdd","tid":338923,"uid":48460,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有D仲衰<br />\ncut到一半先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法<br />\n無法例規定轉線一定要打燈<br />\n<br />\n但如果發生意外而又因為你無打燈所導致就係老不<br />\n但都係講句，打個燈好撚難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟不才<br />\n點撚樣可以因爲唔打燈而有交通意外？</blockquote><br />\n講你知唔係唔得<br />\n但你呢啲弱智咪撚考車牌 害死人<br />\nCase 1: cut左右線唔打燈 隔離線以為你純粹挨得埋線繼續俾油去 咁一cut過去-&gt;撞車<br />\nCase 2: 係無燈位嘅馬路可以直行可以右轉 右邊係行人過路處 啲人觀察你架車見你無打燈以為直去所以過路-&gt;撞到人"},{"pid":"c97d69ecfbc3db1d93b489236e81c35d50bfdbf0","tid":338923,"uid":36772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"D 唔打燈既人食撚屎啦<br />\n打個燈好撚難？會好晒油？<br />\n定以為自己係車手係track 上面賽車緊？<br />\n<br />\n打燈有時唔一定係俾車睇，行人都會睇<br />\n<br />\n經常係內街十字路口<br />\nD on9 車手係路口準備出<br />\n轉右又唔打右燈<br />\n搞到直線行人又唔敢過住<br />\n右路口行人又唔敢過住<br />\n左路口想轉左車又唔敢出住<br />\n全世界企定定等你...<br />\n<br />\n做司機定做行人時..見到都會屌出聲<br />\n<br />\n祝唔打<blockquote>引用</blockquote>燈既車手<br />\n死。全。家"},{"pid":"a9c03355a78ad37a9bebc2debe7f1f792e8380d8","tid":338923,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"一定打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打燈&gt;篤油撚篤大油&gt;有位cut<br />\n萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60edbf2eb62da373d3bc0e6845df44cbda00180","tid":338923,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"通常食左身位先打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038edee287ceb703cab8363cb0f86be5902e74af","tid":338923,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常食左身位先打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬆油門 當打燈"},{"pid":"2a67629a84382da8d35ca6486619454c5f1a2deb","tid":338923,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f3dfc357dcbcb7f65722a8b416b0e789f463fd9","tid":338923,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>省電呀大佬</blockquote><br />\n熄冷氣咪仲慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落車推啦撚樣慳油呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2af75ec9074a89d613afd624e89fbf086db7f6","tid":338923,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"cut線通常響安多<br />\n<br />\n利申 住印度"},{"pid":"409b4befb07cd7e08f6b7e660465ba3e22ea546a","tid":338923,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cut線通常響安多<br />\n<br />\n利申 住印度</blockquote><br />\n係越南啲路太窄得兩條線 cut線都係響安"},{"pid":"c348fb70c9f8e9803a6a03bf6d9b75f030072b37","tid":338923,"uid":16949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"通常都係啲的士狗唔打燈<br />\n有時行到路口見到冇車打燈轉入黎就直行架啦<br />\n屌佢老味的士狗就係呢個時候轉入黎<br />\n佢個樣仲要好似係我錯搞到佢要煞車咁<br />\n我直接大大聲屌佢老母"},{"pid":"93f08b1c52d44d5364232cf7e28426224296c388","tid":338923,"uid":5003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 唔打燈既人食撚屎啦<br />\n打個燈好撚難？會好晒油？<br />\n定以為自己係車手係track 上面賽車緊？<br />\n<br />\n打燈有時唔一定係俾車睇，行人都會睇<br />\n<br />\n經常係內街十字路口<br />\nD on9 車手係路口準備出<br />\n轉右又唔打右燈<br />\n搞到直線行人又唔敢過住<br />\n右路口行人又唔敢過住<br />\n左路口想轉左車又唔敢出住<br />\n全世界企定定等你...<br />\n<br />\n做司機定做行人時..見到都會屌出聲<br />\n<br />\n祝唔打<blockquote>引用</blockquote>燈既車手<br />\n死。全。家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有個正常人回覆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e054005803f3721606e7d815deeaa7c82f9fce","tid":338923,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 唔打燈既人食撚屎啦<br />\n打個燈好撚難？會好晒油？<br />\n定以為自己係車手係track 上面賽車緊？<br />\n<br />\n打燈有時唔一定係俾車睇，行人都會睇<br />\n<br />\n經常係內街十字路口<br />\nD on9 車手係路口準備出<br />\n轉右又唔打右燈<br />\n搞到直線行人又唔敢過住<br />\n右路口行人又唔敢過住<br />\n左路口想轉左車又唔敢出住<br />\n全世界企定定等你...<br />\n<br />\n做司機定做行人時..見到都會屌出聲<br />\n<br />\n祝唔打<blockquote>引用</blockquote>燈既車手<br />\n死。全。家</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n真係全世界企定定等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98eb815db9cbf54518c49840c3c97c84370a0c6d","tid":338923,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"好難搵到人入黎9成都死鳩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨返個1成岩岩出車"},{"pid":"d2a8ca082127e9d1d9d8c8dacf4529afa96c6a49","tid":338923,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T21:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有D仲衰<br />\ncut到一半先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw cut線唔打燈好似犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法<br />\n無法例規定轉線一定要打燈<br />\n<br />\n但如果發生意外而又因為你無打燈所導致就係老不<br />\n但都係講句，打個燈好撚難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟不才<br />\n點撚樣可以因爲唔打燈而有交通意外？</blockquote><br />\n有車牌未？"},{"pid":"543657b959428d097cf0d436f690137289a305b1","tid":338923,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T21:09:46.000Z","msg":"<sp